會衍生更多問題"},{"pid":"85816d195d18c573a410dccfa0fc299ab5f7077b","tid":957191,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T00:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9bd2fac75d10b709aa27fd37ba9671a8cdd8bd","tid":957191,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1ae133d99110695c59f7dac8bcd21a8956b389c","tid":957191,"uid":124741,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T00:16:26.000Z","msg":"豬瘟唔係煮熟就冇事咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"若然可以食用，洗鬼<span style=\"color: red;\">坑豬65萬隻</span>？<br />\n<br />\n可以Google紅字<br />\n數目可能更多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd057357bd4ef02703cb04c5d67ed1cbcac685d","tid":957191,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6db73b4401ecf94c01d4f999e00d7de84fe4e5a5","tid":957191,"uid":159876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T00:18:30.000Z","msg":"其實點解一直唔講對人有無影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8QPdyOg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8QPdyOg.png&h=699f7c20&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}